gesic.', 'Others', 'Meperidine and fentanyl should not be used with MAOIs or other agents that possess MAOI activity (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/2567/', '', 'Halothane, Sodium oxybate, Isoflurane, Nitrous oxide, Desflurane, Propofol, Enflurane, Esketamine, Sevoflurane, Etomidate, Naltrexone, More', 'Pertuzumab, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Altretamine, Tagraxofusp, Pegaspargase, Ixazomib, Enasidenib, Porfimer sodium, Niraparib, More', 1767369485);
